{"tid":184771,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線 大人網有5萬個港女會員(雞)","createTime":"2017-04-03T04:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T07:04:42.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2d985e9876e27a6061145f002e90aadb8a6865","tid":184771,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"援交淫網：女會員逾200人　有學生最細17歲 <br />\n警方繼續「雷霆17」反罪惡行動，派臥底搗破會員制援交網站，拘捕23人。新界北總區重案組發現一個名為「hklovely香港少女論壇」網站，向男會員收取高昂會費，以協助男女會員進行援交活動。據悉，男會員中不少為中產以上人士，包括商人及會計。而援交女則有學生，報稱做推銷及美容等行業。網站由2012年開始運作至今5年，會員人數高達10萬人，男女各半 , 得益高達2000萬港元。警方又提及至於為何有達5萬個女會員，相信女子是為了搵快錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sohcradio.com/Media/2015/01/15/20150115_1046_a0201a_57225.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohcradio.com%2FMedia%2F2015%2F01%2F15%2F20150115_1046_a0201a_57225.gif&h=9ea7b55f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f128379c0c9fcfe35aa6d7ecf4b0caf9cc21728","tid":184771,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e844381b7090f9ddb5161cbeab60c505fbaa024","tid":184771,"uid":73689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/184589/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/184589/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d9b5e74debd10fca2fde20b5071271e3d198a397","tid":184771,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"臭雞 全部都係臭雞<br />\n靚既當雞咁屌 屌到厭<br />\n然後結婚搵唔靚既"},{"pid":"f81f7f05793d1903737991a90193e395752c05d2","tid":184771,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"我都係唔溝女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef81c7fe2d3cd749e92e5a2c1c123879a27ed0db","tid":184771,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor